116
00:09:58,973 --> 00:10:00,433
Fine, send me the address.

117
00:10:13,779 --> 00:10:15,781
Honestly, I don't get it.

118
00:10:16,449 --> 00:10:19,702
All the other groups still hang out
after they disband.

119
00:10:19,785 --> 00:10:20,870
But look at us.

120
00:10:21,370 --> 00:10:22,705
We always meet separately.

121
00:10:24,999 --> 00:10:26,000
So?

122
00:10:26,417 --> 00:10:27,835
What's your point?

123
00:10:27,918 --> 00:10:30,963
Frankly, you're the one
I don't get most.

124
00:10:31,047 --> 00:10:32,048
Right.

125
00:10:32,131 --> 00:10:34,800
It's not like Ji-hyeok ending up
at the ER was your fault.

126
00:10:34,884 --> 00:10:37,136
And you filling in
as a substitute host?

127
00:10:37,219 --> 00:10:39,305
Dude, that was ages ago.

128
00:10:41,557 --> 00:10:42,725
You done?

129
00:10:43,893 --> 00:10:45,645
