131
00:10:50,274 --> 00:10:51,275
You know that.

132
00:11:47,415 --> 00:11:49,875
Man, this feels good.

133
00:12:29,165 --> 00:12:31,167
Enjoying the view?

134
00:12:31,625 --> 00:12:34,295
