rather than tell you.

137
00:12:40,593 --> 00:12:41,844
Take a good look.

138
00:12:41,927 --> 00:12:43,429
That's your future.

139
00:12:44,096 --> 00:12:46,265
See the kid in the blue hoodie?

140
00:12:50,561 --> 00:12:52,605
Doesn't he look familiar?

141
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:56,275
When he was a rookie,
his bullying past came out

142
00:12:56,358 --> 00:12:57,985
so his career died instantly.

143
00:12:58,068 --> 00:12:59,695
He was finished.

144
00:12:59,779 --> 00:13:01,614
But people already knew his face.

145
00:13:01,697 --> 00:13:03,866
He was young but had no skills.

146
00:13:03,949 --> 00:13:05,618
Yet he still wanted to party.

147
00:13:05,701 --> 00:13:07,244
So, what happens?

148
00:13:07,328 --> 00:13:10,331
He starts bouncing around clubs,
