155
00:13:53,332 --> 00:13:54,667
I hoped I was wrong.

156
00:13:56,877 --> 00:13:58,379
But it really was you, Ah-jin.

157
00:14:07,179 --> 00:14:08,389
Does Ms. Seo know?

158
00:14:09,890 --> 00:14:12,101
That you're slipping
in and out of VIP rooms?

159
00:14:13,894 --> 00:14:16,438
I didn't want to be there.

160
00:14:17,565 --> 00:14:19,525
