Why do you phrase it like that?

164
00:14:27,449 --> 00:14:29,702
No, why do you live like that?

165
00:14:29,785 --> 00:14:31,078
If you think it's unfair, tell me.

166
00:14:31,161 --> 00:14:33,706
Who summoned you to that VIP room?

167
00:14:38,085 --> 00:14:39,712
Of course, you won't say.

168
00:14:40,921 --> 00:14:41,922
Get out of my car.

169
00:14:47,011 --> 00:14:49,013
You can go to whoever calls you.

170
00:14:53,934 --> 00:14:55,477
I said, get out.

171
