174
00:15:28,677 --> 00:15:29,887
Nothing.

175
00:15:29,970 --> 00:15:32,890
I heard I'd make good money
if I worked for you.

176
00:15:34,558 --> 00:15:35,935
Plus, you're human, too.

177
00:15:36,018 --> 00:15:39,188
There's got to be
something I can learn from you.

178
00:15:39,271 --> 00:15:40,314
What did you say?

179
00:15:42,608 --> 00:15:45,277
I just want to be useful for once.

180
00:15:48,656 --> 00:15:51,575
Anyway, this job.

181
00:15:51,659 --> 00:15:53,369
It's legit, right?

182
00:15:53,452 --> 00:15:55,412
It's not illegal or anything?

183
00:15:55,496 --> 00:15:57,915
You punk. I'm done with that stuff.

184
00:15:57,998 --> 00:16:01,418
We help people who need it
and get paid fair.

185
00:16:02,002 --> 00:16:04,380
And you can find anyone
if you work for me.

186
00:16:04,463 --> 00:16:05,464
Even your girl.

187
00:16:06,465 --> 00:16:07,549
Gosh.

188
00:16:08,008 --> 00:16:09,218
