- We need more kimchi.
- Coming right up.

210
00:17:14,533 --> 00:17:16,118
Ma'am, do you have an empty table?

211
00:17:16,201 --> 00:17:18,746
You'll have to sit with someone else.
Is that okay?

212
00:17:18,829 --> 00:17:19,830
Sure.

213
