214
00:17:37,431 --> 00:17:39,016
One radish soup, please.

215
00:17:39,099 --> 00:17:40,100
Sure thing.

216
00:17:48,859 --> 00:17:52,196
Oh, man. I'm so sorry.

217
00:17:52,279 --> 00:17:53,822
- My bad.
- Be careful.

218
00:17:53,906 --> 00:17:55,824
- I'm really sorry.
- Jeez, never mind.

219
00:18:02,956 --> 00:18:04,333
Gosh.

220
00:18:07,961 --> 00:18:09,088
I apologize.

221
00:18:09,171 --> 00:18:10,172
Forget it.

222
00:18:13,342 --> 00:18:15,719
- I'll pay now.
- Okay.

223
00:18:17,387 --> 00:18:19,640
Thank you for coming.
Have a nice day.

